==[[File:Excalibur.png|frameless]] Early-game [[File:Rune scimitar.png|frameless]]==
Early game content on a combat only pure is built around preparing the account for an extended [[Slayer]] grind and some early bossing. It's recommended to read through the whole early and mid-game sections to understand what account progression will look like through these stages. If you are playing on a [[Ironman Mode|Hardcore Ironman]] or [[Ironman Mode|Ultimate Ironman]] your progression may look slightly different. 

Early-game should be focused on training magic to 55+, getting 43 prayer, obtaining 50 quest points for a slayer block, getting a [[rune scimitar]] from [[Zamorak warrior|Zamorak Warriors]], cash for runes, a [[Dragon defender|Dragon  Defender]], and an [[Amulet of power|Amulet of Power]] or [[Amulet of strength|Amulet of Strength]], along with some useful transportation methods.

''Please pay attention to any [[File:Dungeon icon.png|frameless]] recommendation comments or warnings in the guide linked below.''
{{Main|User:UimSlayOnly/Early-game}}

== [[File:Leaf-bladed sword.png|frameless]] Mid-game [[File:Abyssal whip (My Arm's Big Adventure).png|frameless]] ==
Mid-game content is built around unlocking your final gear required for efficient Slayer on a combat only pure. There's a lot of different options and routes you can take at this stage but it is recommended to acquire all the following gear at some point unless you're an [[Ironman Mode|Ultimate Ironman]]. 

If you followed the early-game portion closely you should have a Magic level of 55 or more, a Prayer level of 43 or more, access to the [[Warriors' Guild]] with a [[Rune defender|rune]] or [[dragon defender]], a [[rune scimitar]] and [[Excalibur]], and access to many transportation options. If you did any clues or [[crazy archaeologist]] you might have a [[Amulet of strength|strength]], [[Amulet of power|power]], and [[Amulet of magic|magic amulet]]. If you didn't get lucky with clues you will get those during this stage.  

This stage of the game is heavily gear focused so the main goals should be getting 55/70/85 slayer for weapon upgrades, doing minigames like [[Barbarian Assault|barbarian assault]] or [[Pest Control|pest control]] for armour, [[fire cape]], [[God capes|imbued god cape]], and hard clue loot with some mid-tier bossing.  

''Please pay attention to any [[File:Dungeon icon.png|frameless]] recommendation comments or warnings in the guide linked below.''

{{Main|User:UimSlayOnly/Mid-game}}

== [[File:Abyssal tentacle.png|frameless]] End-game [[File:Ghrazi rapier.png|frameless]] ==

End-game content on a combat only pure consists of reaching max total level combat pure, unlocking your final slayer bosses like [[kraken]], [[thermonuclear smoke devil]], and [[Alchemical Hydra]] for the gear they drop. There are a lot of completionist goals that will come into play at this stage of the account including the [[Champion's cape]], [[infernal cape]], [[Nightmare of Ashihama]], more clues, and Raiding.

This section lists many more things like every available pet, raiding tips, bossing tips, and unique grinds that are available to combat only pures.

''Please pay attention to any [[File:Dungeon icon.png|frameless]] recommendation comments or warnings in the guide linked below.''

{{Main|User:UimSlayOnly/End-game}}

